┬In loving memory of
Sonja Arnold
1963-2018
Those who sow in tears will reap with songs of joy.
Those who go out weeping will return with songs
of joy, carrying sheaves with them.
Psalm 126"╠
╔IN MEMORY OF A DARLING SON, BROTHER AND UNCLE
GOOD FRIEND AND COLLEAGUE
MARIO (JAMES SEABROOK) RICHMOND POSTMAN
29.5.7 ~ 22.04.07
ALWAYS HAPPY, HARD WORKING AND GENEROUS
HE WILL NEVER BE FORGOTTEN"Ń
ÓOCTOBER 5th. 1988
ON OCT. 5th. 1938 IN HANKOW. CHINA
DAVID AND WINIFRED GUNN WERE MARRIED
AND TODAY WITH GREAT JOY
THEY CELEBRATE FIFTY GOLDEN YEARS

OCTOBER 5TH 1993
EMERALD WEDDING ANNIVERSARY
FIVE MORE HAPPY YEARS"Ń
